OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPrayagraj Magh mela:       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FThousands head for Hindu   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffestival amid Covid surge  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of Hindu pilgrims have begun 
OL,6, arriving in the northern Indian city of
OL,7, Prayagraj (formerly Allahabad) for a   
OL,8, festival amid a massive surge in       
OL,9, Covid-19 infections.                   
OL,11,FDevotees believe that bathing in the   
OL,12,Friver Ganges during the Makar Sankranti
OL,13,Ffestival would cleanse their sins.     
OL,15,FA similar gathering had contributed to 
OL,16,FIndia's deadly second wave last year.  
OL,18,FBut the authorities in Uttar Pradesh   
OL,19,Fstate, where Prayagraj is located, have
OL,20,Frefused to ban this year's event.      
